sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as Service A (Sender)
    participant G as AXME Cloud
    participant B as Service B (Recipient)
    participant W as Webhook Consumer

    A ->> G: POST /v1/intents (HTTPS)
    G -->> A: 201 accepted + intent_id

    G ->> B: route via registry / runtime

    alt encrypted transport
        G ->> B: encrypted envelope
        B ->> B: decrypt and execute
    else direct internal delivery
        G ->> B: plain payload delivery
    else delivery failed
        G ->> G: retry / backoff schedule
    end

    B -->> G: progress / completion event
    G -->> A: status update visible via GET

    opt webhook enabled
        G ->> W: signed webhook notification
        alt 2xx accepted
            W -->> G: ok
        else non-2xx
            W -->> G: error
            G ->> G: webhook retry policy
        end
    end
